---

This project adapts the Jaffle Shop sample data and dbt models originally
published by dbt Labs (https://github.com/dbt-labs/jaffle-shop), also under
Apache 2.0. Semantic definitions, DQL blocks, and notebooks in this repo are
new work layered on top of that seed.
